    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1129">
<l>imaippiṟ karappāk kaṟiva laṉaittiṟkē</l>
<l> yētila reṉṉumiv vūr</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I will not wink, knowing that if I did, my lover would hide himself; and for this reason, this town says, he is unloving.</l>
